<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM3.7">
<l>etti ṟattilum yāroṭuṅ kūṭumac</l>
<l>cittan taṉṉait tavirttaṉaṉ ceṅkaṇmāl</l>
<l>atta ṉēyaraṅ kāveṉṟa ḻaikkiṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>pitta ṉāyoḻin tēṉempi rāṉukkē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The red-eyed Māl dispelled that intention to associate with anyone of any nature.</l>
<l>I am calling out saying, ‘O Father!  O Raṅga!’</l>
<l>I have ended up as a madman of our Lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
